+ The Solar_Role_Adapter_File Class

++ Inheritance

* [Solar_Base::HomePage Solar_Base]

 * [Solar_Role_Adapter::HomePage Solar_Role_Adapter]

  * Solar_Role_Adapter_File

++ Overview

Adapter to fetch roles from a Unix-style groups file.

The file format is "group:user1,user2,user3\n".  Example:

<code>
sysadmin:pmjones
writer:pmjones,boshag,agtsmith
editor:pmjones,agtsmith
</code>